# Packages that MUST be in the final APK repository
# regardless of whether they're in skip-ci.list.
#
# Use case: build-essential depends on unversioned gcc, g++, make, binutils,
# libc6-dev metapackages. These are in skip-ci.list (already in silex:slim
# base image) but are critical for end users of the repository. This list
# ensures they make it to repack.list despite skip-ci.list filtering.
#
# One Debian package name per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.

# Build essentials - metapackages needed by build-essential
gcc
g++
make
binutils
libc6-dev
